	<div style="text-align:right;">
		CASTRO, Gabriel Henrique de<sup>1</sup>; VILLANOVA JUNIOR, Jose Ademar<sup>2</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa CNPq-PIBIC		<BR>
